	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.5vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>قَالَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> هَٰذَا رَحۡمَةٞ مِّن رَّبِّيۖ فَإِذَا جَآءَ وَعۡدُ رَبِّي <a data-content='مدكوكا مُسوّى بالأرض' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>جَعَلَهُۥ دَكَّآءَۖ</a> وَكَانَ وَعۡدُ </div><div>رَبِّي</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>حَقّٗا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٨٩ ۞وَتَرَكۡنَا بَعۡضَهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ <a data-content='يختلط ويضطرب' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>يَمُوجُ</a> فِي بَعۡضٖۖ </div><div><a data-content='نفخة البعث' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَنُفِخَ فِي ٱلصُّورِ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَجَمَعۡنَٰهُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> جَمۡعٗا ٩٩ وَعَرَضۡنَا جَهَنَّمَ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ عَرۡضًا </div><div>٠٠١</div></div><div style='font-size:4.6vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلَّذِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> كَانَتۡ أَعۡيُنُهُمۡ فِي <a data-content='غشاء غليظ وستر كثيف' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>غِطَآءٍ</a> عَن ذِكۡرِي وَكَانُواْ لَا يَسۡتَطِيعُونَ </div><div>سَمۡعًا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.7vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>١٠١</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَفَحَسِبَ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوٓاْ أَن يَتَّخِذُواْ عِبَادِي مِن دُونِيٓ أَوۡلِيَآءَۚ </div><div>إِنَّآ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.5vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَعۡتَدۡنَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> جَهَنَّمَ لِلۡكَٰفِرِينَ <a data-content='منزلا أو شيئا يتمتّعون به' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>نُزُلٗا</a> ٢٠١ قُلۡ هَلۡ نُنَبِّئُكُم بِٱلۡأَخۡسَرِينَ </div><div>أَعۡمَٰلًا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.7vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٣٠١</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلَّذِينَ ضَلَّ سَعۡيُهُمۡ فِي ٱلۡحَيَوٰةِ ٱلدُّنۡيَا وَهُمۡ يَحۡسَبُونَ أَنَّهُمۡ </div><div>يُحۡسِنُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>صُنۡعًا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٤٠١ أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ بِ‍َٔايَٰتِ رَبِّهِمۡ وَلِقَآئِهِۦ </div><div>فَحَبِطَتۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَعۡمَٰلُهُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَلَا نُقِيمُ لَهُمۡ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ <a data-content='مقدارا واعتبارا لحبوط أعمالهم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَزۡنٗا</a> ٥٠١ ذَٰلِكَ جَزَآؤُهُمۡ </div><div>جَهَنَّمُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.7vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِمَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> كَفَرُواْ وَٱتَّخَذُوٓاْ ءَايَٰتِي وَرُسُلِي هُزُوًا ٦٠١ إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ </div><div>وَعَمِلُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> كَانَتۡ لَهُمۡ جَنَّٰتُ <a data-content='أعلى الجنّة وأوسطها وأفضلها' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ٱلۡفِرۡدَوۡسِ</a> نُزُلًا ٧٠١ خَٰلِدِينَ </div><div>فِيهَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.7vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يَبۡغُونَ عَنۡهَا <a data-content='تحوّلا وانتقالا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>حِوَلٗا</a> ٨٠١ قُل لَّوۡ كَانَ ٱلۡبَحۡرُ <a data-content='هو المّادة التي يكتب بها' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>مِدَادٗا</a> <a data-content='معلوماته وحكمته تعالى' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>لِّكَلِمَٰتِ رَبِّي</a> </div><div><a data-content='فنيَ وفَرغ' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>لَنَفِدَ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.7vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡبَحۡرُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> قَبۡلَ أَن تَنفَدَ كَلِمَٰتُ رَبِّي وَلَوۡ جِئۡنَا بِمِثۡلِهِۦ <a data-content='عونا وزيادة' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>مَدَدٗا</a> ٩٠١ قُلۡ </div><div>إِنَّمَآ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.7vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَنَا۠</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> بَشَرٞ مِّثۡلُكُمۡ يُوحَىٰٓ إِلَيَّ أَنَّمَآ إِلَٰهُكُمۡ إِلَٰهٞ وَٰحِدٞۖ فَمَن كَانَ </div><div>يَرۡجُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لِقَآءَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> رَبِّهِۦ فَلۡيَعۡمَلۡ عَمَلٗا صَٰلِحٗا وَلَا يُشۡرِكۡ بِعِبَادَةِ رَبِّهِۦٓ أَحَدَۢا </div><div>٠١١</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
